data.description:
VA ASSUMABLE 2.50% LOAN  makes this a unique opportunity for savvy buyers. Impeccably maintained and barely lived in, it awaits new owners! This stunning 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom gem boasts a generous 1966 square feet of living space, embracing a spacious open concept that seamlessly blends style and comfort. Built in 2019, this home offers modern living at its finest.
Step into the heart of the home, where the kitchen takes center stage with gleaming granite countertops and an island with tons of counter space and cabinets! Two dining areas cater to both intimate family dinners and larger gatherings, creating a versatile space for entertaining. The thoughtful split floor plan ensures privacy, with the master suite offering a serene retreat. The two additional bedrooms provide ample space for family, guests, or a home office, accommodating your lifestyle needs. Did I mention storage space!!! This home is loaded with more than enough storage space for your belongings! Beyond the interiors, discover the large backyard with a covered patio, setting the scene for lively celebrations, or quiet moments of relaxation. The front and back yards are fully irrigated, ensuring a lush and vibrant landscape year-round. Located on a quite cul-de-sac!
Don't miss out on the chance to call this residence yours. Schedule a viewing today and step into this beautiful home and see for yourself every detail that this home offers! Seller to included in the sale of the Washer/Dryer and Refrigerator! This home is conveniently located close to all that New Braunfels has to offer, including downtown, Gruene and Creekside shopping area! Call for more details!
